These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, analyst, project-manager, lawyer
1. the lawyer is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
4. the project-manager is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Job        | entrepreneur | analyst   | lawyer | project-manager    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, aconite, daffodil, sunflower
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Flower   | sunflower    | balloon-flower | daffodil | aconite    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, azalea, begonia, balloon-flower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person who growsbegonia is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Flower          | balloon-flower | begonia | azalea    | aconite      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, azure, red, emerald
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who likes lavender and the person who likes emerald##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who likes red is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Color   | red       | lavender   | azure    | emerald  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
4 different pets are kept: frog, mouse, goat, fish
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
2. the owner of the mouse is the fan of punk##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
6. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Pet   | frog | fish | goat | mouse |

 #################################

 
