4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| Hobby   | baking | dancing     | card-games  | cooking  |

