.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, mystery, western
4 different games are played: bridge, go, monopoly, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
6. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| Game     | mah-jongg | monopoly  | bridge     | go |

