.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, chinese, american, indonesian
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the chinese##3
2. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
4. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the french is between the indonesian and the chinese##2
6. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the fish is between the french and the owner of the goat##2
8. the french is on the left or right of the chinese##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Nationality   | chinese | french      | indonesian | american |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

