.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
City: boston, hamburg, miami, marseilles
1. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person eating pepper##2
4. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating pepper is the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| City    | marseilles     | hamburg | boston     | miami  |

