.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, mexican, brazilian, french
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, french-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the indonesian##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is french-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is french-polo is on the left of the brazilian##1
5. the mexican is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality   | indonesian   | french   | mexican      | brazilian      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | french-polo | biathlon |

