.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
House: victorian, wooden, ranch-style, art-deco
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goat, snake
1. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
2. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
3. the art-deco house is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the victorian house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
6. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| House   | ranch-style | art-deco | victorian | wooden |
| Pet           | snake     | dog     | goat   | frog         |

