.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, black, grey, light-blue
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who likes red is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who likes black##2
2. the person who likes grey is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes black##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Color   | light-blue | black         | red   | grey |
| Sport   | soccer    | skateboarding | weightlifting | ice-hockey   |

