.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, go, whist, bridge
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, nigerian, turkish
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
3. the japanese is the person playing whist##1
4. the nigerian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the japanese is between the turkish and the nigerian##2
6. the person playing go is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Game         | bridge   | whist | backgammon | go    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | japanese  | turkish     | american |

