.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, ice-hockey, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, tram, trike
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Sport   | basketball | ice-hockey | baseball  | tennis |
| Transport     | bus      | tram       | motorbike | trike     |

