.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, software-developer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, musical, sports, adventure
1. the manager is in an even position##4
2. the manager is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
3. the person watching musical movies is between the entrepreneur and the person watching zombie movies##2
4. the manager is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the software-developer##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur | pilot   | software-developer | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure          | musical | zombie         | sports  |

 